text: Jennifer Morrison (n√©e Warren; born 8 January 1968) is the wife of Scott Morrison, the 30th Prime Minister of Australia. Morrison is a registered nurse. She was born in Canterbury, New South Wales and grew up in Peakhurst, Sydney. She and her husband first met at the age of 12, started dating at 16 and were married at 21. The couple have two children. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Australian nurses Category:People from Sydney
